{"tid":688572,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人理應學識光合作用","createTime":"2018-06-03T11:01:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-03T14:29:31.000Z","uid":8830,"like":5,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"85207fdd3ee252780793fc46dbfff44d80a4e672","tid":688572,"uid":8830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T11:01:01.000Z","msg":"首先我睇到呢個post<br />\n<br />\n「大家一齊數下香港餐廳有咩小聰明????<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/687388/page/1?ref=ios」\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/687388/page/1?ref=ios」</a><br />\n<br />\n講到香港既餐廳好多度縮野黑暗野<br />\n食物質素又差仲要貴<br />\n咁唔係香港餐廳食野<br />\n似乎合情合理<br />\n<br />\n然後我再睇到呢個post<br />\n「究竟幾時開始喺支那食嘢變咗潮流？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/687774/page/1?ref=ios」\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/687774/page/1?ref=ios」</a><br />\n<br />\n先利申我有飲過喜茶食過椰子雞打過牛肉邊爐<br />\n乾唔乾淨 有冇儲齊元素表 對身體有咩影響暫時答你唔到<br />\n唯一答到你既係食物質素比香港高<br />\n價錢亦都係比較平<br />\n原諒我窮撚冇能力去高質貴價米芝連餐廳用餐<br />\n係香港我負擔得起而好食既餐廳少之又少<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(或者係我見識少，歡迎留言推薦好餐廳)<br />\n小店又講到一文不值<br />\n食m記又話我食支那雞肉<br />\n食譚仔之類米線類又話一滴香味精難食<br />\n北上食野又講到賣港咁嚴重<br />\n咁對唔住喇連登仔<br />\n我出返去學光合作用先喇"},{"pid":"20f085496f6e0e4ac61bb8e158cb5f275e28b3b5","tid":688572,"uid":54181,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T11:02:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8c2bafa1d9412ea62a9bbb57dcf63a8795e1e417","tid":688572,"uid":8830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T11:03:02.000Z","msg":"補返條link<br />\n打多左個引號<br />\n<br />\n大家一齊數下香港餐廳有咩小聰明????<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/687388/page/1?ref=ios\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/687388/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n<br />\n究竟幾時開始喺支那食嘢變咗潮流？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/687774/page/1?ref=ios\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/687774/page/1?ref=ios</a>"},{"pid":"337314667c97dee8df6e33cb497c7dce996cd11c","tid":688572,"uid":17859,